Interface PersistentEObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EObject, InternalEObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPersistentEObject

    public interface PersistentEObject
extends InternalEObject
    An EObject identified by a unique Id, able to persist in datastores.
